		<hr size="1">Basically, I'm wondering how the economy on this relatively new server compares to other servers. Did so many twinks "move-log" over that our economy was blown to hell before it ever had a chance?</P><P>I say this as a true newbie (played the game for just over a month, my "high level" is a 16 enchanter). As a newbie, I am constantly strapped for cash... </P><P>...actually I think always scrounging for cash is a cool part of the game. Makes one have to think. But, I digress...</P><P>I always see people in EC auctioning things that are outlandishly expensive. They are to me at least (I've never had more than 24pp saved up at any one time). Have you people with all this cash actually earned it on this server or did you move-log over?</P><P>I guess its not too big of a deal, I love this game and will probably play until I can twink a char or 3 but, on the other hand, I like the idea of struggling along and feeling like my group mates are in the same boat.</P><P>Just a ramble as I wait for the !$#$& patch to finish.</P><P>Vileran<BR>16 DE Enchanter</P><P><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
