		<hr size="1">The smartest things said in this thread are 1) do good deeds for others and 2) learn to haggle.  I've made thousands of pp in the auction "trade," and it started with doing good deeds for higher lev folks (not asskissing, just helping if I see people in trouble).  From the few gifts I was given I made a few hundred plat.  This led to my watching the auction prices in EC, which led to my buying my first item CHEAP and selling it HIGH, and so on and so on.  This is the best way to make money in EQ.  It will absorb a lot of your playing time, and is non-productive other than making $$$ (sitting in the tunnel auctioning), but you will get to know important people and have great gear at levels lower than others.  Cheers!<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
	</font>
